<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Joe Lund's | Dr. Joseph Luyindadio</title>
    
    <style>
        /* CONFIGURATION DU DÉFILEMENT */
        html {
            scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #0b132b;
        }

        section {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* FENÊTRE 1 : ACCUEIL */
        .window-home {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 32, 74, 0.7), rgba(0, 32, 74, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516549655169-df83a0774514?q=80&w=2000');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .window-home h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* FENÊTRE 2 : LE DOCTEUR (Avec ta photo joe.jpg) */
        .window-doctor {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #1c2541;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 60px;
            padding: 0 10%;
        }

        .doctor-photo {
            width: 380px;
            height: 500px;
            background: #ccc url('joe.jpg') no-repeat center;
            background-size: cover;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 25px 25px 0px #00cba9;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease; /* Transition pour le zoom */
        }

        .doctor-photo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Effet de zoom au survol */
        }

        .doctor-info {
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 550px;
        }

        .doctor-info h2 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #004a99;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* FENÊTRE 3 : SERVICES */
        .window-tech {
            background: #f0f4f8;
        }

        .tech-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .tech-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-bottom: 5px solid #00cba9;
        }

        /* FENÊTRE 4 : CONTACT WHATSAPP */
        .window-contact {
            background: #004a99;
            color: white;
        }

        .whatsapp-btn {
            background-color: #25D366;
            color: white;
            padding: 22px 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .whatsapp-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.08);
            background-color: #1ebe57;
        }

        /* Icône de défilement */
        .scroll-hint {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {transform: translateY(0);}
            40% {transform: translateY(-10px);}
            60% {transform: translateY(-5px);}
        }

        /* Adaptabilité Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .window-doctor { flex-direction: column; height: auto; padding: 50px 20px; }
            .doctor-photo { width: 280px; height: 350px; margin: 0 auto; }
            .doctor-info { text-align: center; }
            .window-home h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="window-home">
        <h1>JOE LUND'S</h1>
        <p>Imagerie Médicale par le Dr. Joseph Luyindadio</p>
        <div class="scroll-hint">↓</div>
    </section>

    <section class="window-doctor">
        <div class="doctor-photo"></div>
        <div class="doctor-info">
            <span style="color: #00cba9; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">Expertise & Rigueur</span>
            <h2>Dr. Joseph Luyindadio</h2>
            <p>Fondateur de <strong>Joe Lund's</strong>, le Dr. Luyindadio met son expertise en imagerie médicale au service de votre santé à Kinshasa.</p>
            <p>Spécialisé dans le diagnostic de haute précision, il vous accompagne avec professionnalisme et bienveillance.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="window-tech">
        <h2 style="color: #004a99; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 40px;">Nos Services</h2>
        <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech-card">
                <h3>RADIOGRAPHIE</h3>
                <p>Imagerie numérique pour un diagnostic osseux et pulmonaire précis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-card">
                <h3>ÉCHOGRAPHIE</h3>
                <p>Examens spécialisés (Doppler, 4D, Abdominal) en temps réel.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-card">
                <h3>SCANNER</h3>
                <p>Exploration approfondie avec une technologie ultra-rapide.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="window-contact">
        <h2 style="font-size: 3rem; margin: 0;">Prendre Rendez-vous</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 20px 0 40px;">Contactez-nous directement sur WhatsApp pour une réponse immédiate.</p>
        
        <a href="https://wa.me/243898392289?text=Bonjour%20Dr%20Joseph%20Luyindadio,%20je%20souhaite%20prendre%20rendez-vous%20au%20cabinet%20Joe%20Lund's." 
           class="whatsapp-btn">
            RESERVER VIA WHATSAPP
        </a>

        <div style="margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding-top: 20px;">
            <p>📍 Gombe, Kinshasa | 📞 089 839 2289</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7;">&copy; 2026 Joe Lund's - Tous droits réservés.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
